title: [SOLVED]MACBOOK AIR , 820 3435 B Don't enter IOS
message:
Check verbose mode. Run EFI ASD, check for liquid.
Actually this is also very common on ones where the BIOS was messed with.

message:
[url]https://drive.google.com/open?id=0ByfhQ_x0v-tZODBwSkdwYjhnaFE[/url]
